---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Off the Rails
description: Engineering with a neurodivergent brain. Honest about the walls. Occasionally useful about the workarounds.
pagination:
  data: collections.offTheRails
  size: 999
  alias: posts
eleventyExcludeFromCollections: true
---

<section class="listing-header listing-header--off-the-rails">
  <div class="listing-header-inner">
    <span class="persona-tag persona-tag--off-the-rails">Off the Rails</span>
    <h1 class="listing-title">Off the Rails</h1>
    <p class="listing-byline">with Pliny, the Moderately Informed</p>
    <p class="listing-desc">
      Engineering with a neurodivergent brain. Honest about the walls.
      Occasionally useful about the workarounds.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="listing-posts">
  <div class="listing-posts-inner">
    {% set published = [] %}
    {% for post in collections.offTheRails | reverse %}
      {% if not post.data.draft %}
        {% set published = published.concat([post]) %}
      {% endif %}
    {% endfor %}

    {% if published.length %}
      <ul class="listing-list">
        {% for post in published %}
        <li class="listing-item">
          <a href="{{ post.url | prefix }}" class="listing-item-link">
            <div class="listing-item-meta">
              <span class="listing-item-date">{{ post.date | readableDate }}</span>
              {% if post.data.linkedin %}
                <span class="linkedin-flag">Also on LinkedIn</span>
              {% endif %}
            </div>
            <h2 class="listing-item-title">{{ post.data.title }}</h2>
            {% if post.data.description %}
              <p class="listing-item-desc">{{ post.data.description }}</p>
            {% endif %}
          </a>
        </li>
        {% endfor %}
      </ul>
    {% else %}
      <div class="listing-empty">
        <p>First post incoming. Stack is chosen.</p>
        <p class="listing-empty-sub">Check back after April 2026.</p>
      </div>
    {% endif %}
  </div>
</section>
